       - `spendCredits(userId, amount, reason, referenceId)` transactional
         - Use `UPDATE subscriptions SET current_credits = current_credits - $amount WHERE user_id = $userId AND current_credits >= $amount RETURNING *` to prevent negative balances without explicit row locking
       - `addCredits(userId, amount, reason, referenceId)` transactional
       - `getCredits(userId)`
       - log every mutation in `credit_transactions`
       - All credit mutations run in `SERIALIZABLE` or `REPEATABLE READ` isolation to prevent race conditions
